image_analysis.description: A nighttime photograph of a narrow outdoor balcony or terrace. The space features light-colored stone tiling on the floor and a matching stone wall on the right. Several large, rectangular grey planters containing pink and dried flowers are visible. In the background, there is a small bistro-style table with two dark wicker-style high-top chairs. A wall-mounted lantern and a doorway are visible on the right wall. The background beyond the balcony railing is dark, showing outlines of other buildings.
image_analysis.layout: Vertical orientation showing a perspective view down the length of a balcony.
